01:16:07.430 --> 01:16:09.680
know who the likely voters are?

01:16:09.680 --> 01:16:11.690
Because it's changing,
as you speak,

01:16:11.690 --> 01:16:13.490
through deliberate
action, and through

01:16:13.490 --> 01:16:15.140
the action of the politicians.

01:16:15.140 --> 01:16:17.235
- We got it all wrong in 2016.

01:16:17.235 --> 01:16:20.550
- Well, everyone's like,
remember when Alexandria

01:16:20.550 --> 01:16:21.361
Ocasio-Cortez won?

01:16:21.361 --> 01:16:21.860
[GASPS]

