She beat 10-term Crowley.

01:16:24.262 --> 01:16:25.220
It was out of the blue.

01:16:25.220 --> 01:16:26.890
No it wasn't, buddy.

01:16:26.890 --> 01:16:31.040
Because she had a strategy
of expanding the electorate,

01:16:31.040 --> 01:16:33.110
and the pollsters missed it.

01:16:33.110 --> 01:16:36.410
And they missed Andrew
Gillum in the primary.

01:16:36.410 --> 01:16:41.570
He was the only non-millionaire
in a field of five.

01:16:41.570 --> 01:16:43.640
And for sure, they
thought he had no chance.

01:16:43.640 --> 01:16:46.985
Black guy who's
mayor of Tallahassee

01:16:46.985 --> 01:16:48.110
trying to run for governor.

01:16:48.110 --> 01:16:50.000
No way he's getting
through the primary.

