01:19:07.610 --> 01:19:11.210
mobilized the base of
the Republican Party.

01:19:11.210 --> 01:19:14.000
And it looks like
the president still

01:19:14.000 --> 01:19:18.534
has a lot of cause for optimism,
because the Democrats also--

01:19:18.534 --> 01:19:20.075
even though they
lost the House, this

01:19:20.075 --> 01:19:21.491
is going to be a
ready-made excuse

01:19:21.491 --> 01:19:24.250
to explain why his
agenda won't pass,

01:19:24.250 --> 01:19:26.750
whereas he had a harder time
explaining when they controlled

01:19:26.750 --> 01:19:29.330
both houses of the Congress.

01:19:29.330 --> 01:19:31.800
So the president still has
a lot of cause for optimism,

01:19:31.800 --> 01:19:32.300
doesn't he?

01:19:32.300 --> 01:19:32.690
- Yeah.

01:19:32.690 --> 01:19:33.850
I think that was
Sarah's point, right?

01:19:33.850 --> 01:19:34.683
- That was my point.

01:19:34.683 --> 01:19:35.630
- Yeah.

01:19:35.630 --> 01:19:36.425
Thank you, though.

01:19:36.425 --> 01:19:38.450
- Yes.

01:19:38.450 --> 01:19:38.950
- Hi.

01:19:38.950 --> 01:19:43.420
