I go to things like this

01:19:43.420 --> 01:19:45.010
as much as I can,
and I have to say,

01:19:45.010 --> 01:19:47.890
this has been a really,
really good one.

01:19:47.890 --> 01:19:49.407
Thank you all for that.

01:19:49.407 --> 01:19:49.990
- I like that.

01:19:49.990 --> 01:19:51.349
