01:26:09.990 --> 01:26:10.830
40 million people.

01:26:10.830 --> 01:26:13.290
We only have two senators,
and so does Rhode Island.

01:26:13.290 --> 01:26:14.530
Now, why is that fair?

01:26:14.530 --> 01:26:15.570
So he says that.

