But he also says, publicly
finance every single campaign,

01:26:21.330 --> 01:26:24.780
so that we take money
out so that we bring

01:26:24.780 --> 01:26:26.400
the public back into service.

01:26:26.400 --> 01:26:27.750
I like that idea.

01:26:27.750 --> 01:26:29.711
It's a good article.

01:26:29.711 --> 01:26:30.210
- Great.

01:26:30.210 --> 01:26:32.430
Thank you so much to
all of our panelists.

